{
  "macro_id": "telecommunications.costPerLine",
  "domain": "telecommunications",
  "name": "costPerLine",
  "reads_artifact_data": true,
  "inputs": {
    "infrastructureCost": {
      "type": "number",
      "required": false
    },
    "monthlyOpsCost": {
      "type": "number",
      "required": false
    },
    "subscribers": {
      "type": "number",
      "required": false
    },
    "arpu": {
      "type": "number",
      "required": false
    }
  },
  "invariants": [
    "typeof output === 'object' && output !== null",
    "typeof output.ok === 'boolean'",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.subscribers)",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.arpu)",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.costPerSubscriber)",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.margin)",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.marginPercent)",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.profitable === 'boolean'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.breakeven === 'string'",
    "output.ok === true || typeof (output.error || output.message) === 'string'"
  ],
  "fuzz_cases": [
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "infrastructureCost": 600000,
            "monthlyOpsCost": 50000,
            "subscribers": 10000,
            "arpu": 50
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "infrastructureCost": 6000000,
            "monthlyOpsCost": 100000,
            "subscribers": 1000,
            "arpu": 50
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "infrastructureCost": 1200000,
        "monthlyOpsCost": 30000,
        "subscribers": 5000,
        "arpu": 40
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {},
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "infrastructureCost": "1e999",
            "monthlyOpsCost": "NaN",
            "subscribers": "0",
            "arpu": "Infinity"
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": false
      }
    }
  ],
  "_note": "LENS_ACTIONS handler (path-3; NOT assassin-enumerated). COMPONENT-EXACT shape: panel sends {artifact:{data:{infrastructureCost,monthlyOpsCost,subscribers,arpu}}}; dispatch peels the wrapper. RETURNS subscribers/arpu/costPerSubscriber/margin/marginPercent/profitable/breakeven — the exact keys the CostResult card renders. costPerSubscriber = (infra/60 + ops)/subscribers; margin = arpu - costPerSub. subscribers parseInt||1 so a '0' floors to 1 (no /0). POISON: infra/ops/arpu via num() so 'Infinity'/'1e999'/'NaN' collapse to finite defaults; margin + marginPercent stay FINITE. Pure compute, no STATE. Pinned by server/tests/telecommunications-lens-macros.test.js."
}
